{"tid":188152,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"迷雲若我 繼續情願熱戀 發誓重奪第一的老","createTime":"2017-04-05T12:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T04:34:19.000Z","uid":42982,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d284f29dcfaac8c80e252bb86284903753c88f07","tid":188152,"uid":42982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://68.media.tumblr.com/ecd91a0a081f9385f5011a204a2f1718/tumblr_inline_onxkuhN6U91ueqzi5_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2Fecd91a0a081f9385f5011a204a2f1718%2Ftumblr_inline_onxkuhN6U91ueqzi5_1280.jpg&h=3d18f7a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨近季尾夜已深　易帥一刻多麼接近<br />\n飛機天際在疑問　矛盾也更深<br />\n從未確信會競爭　別了Big Four 終不靠近<br />\n爭標掙扎及遺憾　偷偷的再生<br />\n迷雲內閧　眼望前路落空<br />\n再遇球員流失的暗湧<br />\n不要　不要　不要驟來驟去<br />\n這一季～又告終<br />\n迷雲若我<br />\n繼續情願熱戀　發誓重奪第一的老翁<br />\n這秒鐘　搶一分　都劇痛"},{"pid":"e5720a94db673024323c0e1f0c84c2ce4941db4c","tid":188152,"uid":42982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa39a8aebaf64902912b27de43aa3d56af7ff82","tid":188152,"uid":42982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3e8e701fa625f8d041e06e2e641f22b9e749d5","tid":188152,"uid":8781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:46:44.000Z","msg":"受傷的女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35183c50ff303028ab10bb80465537bb826f1d5","tid":188152,"uid":42982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T14:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b3fb86ef132797fa1310b6c8ff7e6d20dec33d","tid":188152,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"高汁<